         <div type="edition" ana="#b5" subtype="transcription" xml:id="beth0163.transcription" corresp="#beth0163.translation">
            <p>Ὃς ἐὰν μεταθῇ ταύτην ὁ ἐπανγιλάμενος<lb/> ζωποιῆσε τοὺς νεκροὺς<lb/> αὐτὸς
                  κρινε<supplied reason="omitted">ι</supplied>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b5" xml:id="beth0163.translation" corresp="#beth0163.transcription">
            <p>Anyone who changes this lady's place (i.e., the woman buried in this grave), He
					who promised to resurrect the dead will Himself judge (him).</p>
         </div>
      </body>
